Update system and pip

sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y python3-pip python3-numpy
pip3 install --upgrade pip --no-cache-dir

Install core packages (exact working versions Jan 2026 validated)
pip3 install skyfield==1.49 numpy==1.26.4 folium==0.15.1 xyzservices==2025.11.0 requests==2.31.0 --no-cache-dir

Verify installation
python3 -c "from skyfield.api import load, EarthSatellite, wgs84; import folium; import xyzservices.providers as xyz; print('All packages loaded - tracker ready')"

